<i>noun</i>: 피동 [피ː동] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>피동 [피ː동]</dt><br>
<dd>1. passiveness</dd><br>
<dd>스스로 움직이지 않고 남의 힘에 의해 움직임.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being moved by someone’s power, not by one’s own.</dd><br>
<dd>2. passive voice</dd><br>
<dd>주어가 남의 힘에 의해 움직이는 동사의 성질.</dd><br>
<dd>A property of verbs indicating that the subject is moved by someone's power.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>